      • evaluateParams

        protected io.permazen.parse.expr.AbstractInvokeNode.ParamInfo evaluateParams(ParseSession session)
        Evaluate parameters and parameter types.

        TypeInferringNodes are not evaluated, instead they are left as null and the corresponding parameter type is set to the special value MethodUtil.FunctionalType. Null parameters have their parameter type set to MethodUtil.NullType.

        Parameters:
        session - parse session
        Returns:
        evaluated parameter info
